snippet.title: Yule Sock Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Yule Sock is a singleplayer, retro, 8-bit, arcade game created in PICO-8. The goal is to collect fruits and sweets dropped by Santa with – guess what? – a yule sock. The minigame has an offline highscore, so that you can challenge your friends, for even more fun.
